<blockquote class="messageText SelectQuoteContainer ugc baseHtml">
<div class="bbCodeBlock bbCodeQuote" data-author="eaglejarl">
<aside>
<div class="attribution type">eaglejarl said:
<a href="goto/post?id=5518171#post-5518171" class="AttributionLink">&uarr;</a>
</div>
<blockquote class="quoteContainer"><div class="quote">On the other hand, y&#039;all have exactly two game balance mechanics: food and the fact that you have no hands. I&#039;m reluctant to take away one of those things.<br/>
</div><div class="quoteExpand">Click to expand...</div></blockquote>
</aside>
</div>You missed one, and I hate myself for drawing your attention to it: Mana bonds.<br/>
Chaos Shifts destroy tapped mana bonds, even if it&#039;s only a 1% chance per tapped bond, we start loosing a tapped bond nearly every turn once we get to 75 bonds. At 5% it&#039;s a loss every 20 tapped bonds. This forces us to spend them carefully, and waste actions reacquiring bonds for what we&#039;ve lost.
<div class="messageTextEndMarker">&nbsp;</div>
</blockquote>
